Relations between us and the <span style="color: #7A3C00;">communists</span> are tense, ever since the shift of our party to the right and the subsequent departure of Stahler. However, we can still take efforts to reduce the level of hostility between us.

@cps_2
on-arrival: cps_relation += 10*(1 - dissent); cps_hostility -= 1

As the level of hostility between us and the <span style="color: #7A3C00;">communists</span> has significantly reduced, this has made improvement of relations much easier.

