@ind_cooperative
on-arrival: ind_relation += 5*(1 - dissent)

Due to our commitment to <span style="color: #D3C24D;">bludish</span> rights, the independents are more inclined to cooperate with us. However, our capitalist platform is slowing down our efforts.

@ind_hostile
on-arrival: ind_relation += 2*(1 - dissent)

The electing of Harringston has turned the independents against us, who are wary of our lack of support for equal rights of the <span style="color: #D3C24D;">bludish</span> people. This is making fostering of good will almost impossible. 

@ind_friendly
on-arrival: ind_relation += 8*(1 - dissent); ind_hostility -= 1

Manoly's views are aligned closely with those of the independents, so relation building is more efficient.

@wpb
