@wpb_cooperative
on-arrival: wpb_relation += 8*(1 - dissent); wpb_hostility -= 1

We have succesfully reduced the tensions between our parties. Improving relations comes much more easily than before. 

@wpb_unfriendly
on-arrival: wpb_relation += 5*(1 - dissent); wpb_hostility -= 1

The low level of trust between us and the <span style="color: #D3C24D;">WPB</span> makes building friendly relations difficult, but not impossible.

@wpb_hostile
on-arrival: wpb_relation += 2*(1 - dissent)

Sebastian has shown a rather opposing stance to advancing <span style="color: #D3C24D;">Bludish</span> rights, making any sort of cooperation between us and the WPB implausible.

@pfjp_alone

Whether it is because we *cannot* or *will not*, we do not make ties with other parties at this moment.

